308
00:17:44,204 --> 00:17:45,604
Marshall.

309
00:17:46,404 --> 00:17:48,404
Prazer em te conhecer, Marshall.

310
00:17:48,604 --> 00:17:50,304
Somos colegas então?

311
00:17:50,604 --> 00:17:51,804
